# CosmicTrotter - Netlify Redirects & Rewrites
# Clean URLs + security + fallback for static multi-page site

# === Clean URL Rewrites (support nice/canonical extensionless paths) ===
# Must appear early: rewrite clean slug -> actual .html file (200). Exact file matches + these win before the final fallback.
# Home and deep pages with .html in their canonicals work via direct files.
/wisdom                              /wisdom.html                              200
/space                               /space.html                               200
/philosophy                          /philosophy.html                          200
/quantum                             /quantum.html                             200
/ev-guide                            /ev-guide.html                            200
/pm_e-drive_ev_charging_guide        /PM_E-DRIVE_EV_Charging_Guide.html        200

# Friendly aliases for the EV guide (common misspellings/variations)
/pm-e-drive                          /PM_E-DRIVE_EV_Charging_Guide.html        200
/pm-edrive                           /PM_E-DRIVE_EV_Charging_Guide.html        200

# No broad catch-all: unmatched paths will 404 (we provide 404.html below for nice themed error).
# Specific clean URL rewrites + exact files win. Unknown -> real 404.

# === Security Redirects (Block Common Bot Attacks) ===
/wp-admin/*                          /index.html                               301
/wp-login.php                        /index.html                               301
/wp-admin                            /index.html                               301
/wp-admin/install.php                /index.html                               301
/xmlrpc.php                          /index.html                               301
/wp-json/*                           /index.html                               301
/author/*                            /index.html                               301
/comments/*                          /index.html                               301
/.env                                /index.html                               301
/git/*                               /index.html                               301

# === WWW to Non-WWW + HTTPS (force, with !) ===
https://www.cosmictrotter.com/*      https://cosmictrotter.com/:splat          301!

# (Optional) Old hyphenated domain redirect - uncomment if needed
# https://cosmic-trotter.com/*       https://cosmictrotter.com/:splat          301!

# (Telugu fallback is now handled client-side in JS for better UX - dedicated -te.html or Google Translate)